    "Background": {
      "text": "Inflammation of the cervix most commonly caused by\nChlamydia\n(about 40%) and\nGonorrhea\nLess commonly caused by\nTrichomonas\nand\nHSV-2",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
